41 A permittee may appeal the revocation, or nonrenewal revocation of a permit by petitioning
42 a district court judge of the district in which the applicant resides. The determination by the court,
43 on appeal, shall be upon the facts, the law, and the reasonableness of the sheriff's refusal. The
44 determination by the court shall be final for the purpose of appeal."
