22 PART VI. MISCELLANEOUS
23 SECTION 6.1. Prosecutions for offenses committed before the effective date of this
24 act are not abated or affected by this act, and the statutes that would be applicable but for this act
25 remain applicable to those prosecutions.
26 SECTION 6.2. Except as otherwise provided, this act is effective when it becomes
27 law.
